{"text_id":161930,"tokens":["The"," advent"," of"," self","-","driving"," cars"," is"," an"," exciting"," development"," in"," the"," automotive"," industry"," that"," holds"," the"," promise"," of"," increased"," safety"," and"," efficiency"," on"," the"," roads","."," However",","," there"," are"," valid"," concerns"," about"," the"," technology","'","s"," safety"," and"," implications",","," especially"," regarding"," traffic"," laws"," and"," passenger"," risks","."," ","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," safety"," concerns"," is"," the"," potential"," for"," accidents","."," Despite"," extensive"," testing"," and"," development",","," self","-","driving"," cars"," are"," not"," yet"," perfect"," and"," can"," malfunction"," or"," make"," errors"," that"," lead"," to"," accidents","."," Hacking"," risks"," are"," also"," a"," concern",","," as"," malicious"," actors"," could"," potentially"," gain"," control"," of"," the"," car","'","s"," systems",","," leading"," to"," dangerous"," situations",".","\n\n","Another"," issue"," is"," the"," reliance"," on"," extensive"," sensor"," technology",","," which"," is"," necessary"," for"," a"," self","-","driving"," car"," to"," function"," properly","."," However",","," these"," sensors"," are"," susceptible"," to"," failure"," or"," interference",","," which"," could"," negatively"," impact"," the"," car","'","s"," performance","."," Additionally",","," there"," is"," a"," concern"," that"," human"," error"," could"," play"," a"," role"," in"," programming"," the"," computer"," systems"," that"," control"," these"," cars",","," leading"," to"," unintended"," consequences"," on"," the"," roads",".","\n\n","From"," a"," traffic"," law"," perspective",","," self","-","driving"," cars"," pose"," a"," unique"," challenge","."," Existing"," traffic"," laws"," are"," primarily"," designed"," for"," human"," drivers",","," and"," it"," may"," be"," difficult"," to"," enforce"," laws"," against"," machines","."," This"," could"," lead"," to"," a"," legal"," grey"," area"," if"," a"," self","-","driving"," car"," violates"," a"," traffic"," law"," or"," causes"," an"," accident",".","\n\n","Lastly",","," considering"," the"," passengers","'"," safety",","," it"," is"," essential"," to"," consider"," the"," risks"," posed"," to"," infants"," and"," other"," vulnerable"," individuals"," who"," may"," not"," have"," the"," ability"," to"," take"," control"," of"," the"," car"," in"," an"," emergency",".","\n\n","While"," self","-","driving"," cars"," have"," the"," potential"," to"," significantly"," impact"," society",","," it"," is"," crucial"," to"," conduct"," thorough"," research"," and"," testing"," to"," ensure"," that"," they"," are"," safe"," and"," secure","."," Manufacturers"," and"," regulators"," must"," address"," these"," concerns"," and"," consider"," different"," perspectives"," to"," gain"," public"," trust"," in"," this"," technology","."," ","\n\n","Advances"," in"," technology"," and"," rigorous"," safety"," standards"," can"," help"," mitigate"," risks",","," but"," it"," is"," essential"," to"," acknowledge"," that"," there"," are"," inherent"," risks"," associated"," with"," self","-","driving"," cars","."," Ultimately",","," it"," is"," the"," responsibility"," of"," manufacturers",","," regulators",","," and"," society"," as"," a"," whole"," to"," strive"," for"," continuous"," improvement"," and"," find"," ways"," to"," minimize"," potential"," dangers","."," ","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," driver","less"," cars"," have"," the"," potential"," to"," revolution","ize"," the"," way"," we"," commute",","," there"," are"," several"," safety"," concerns"," that"," need"," to"," be"," carefully"," addressed"," and"," communicated"," to"," the"," public","."," With"," thorough"," research",","," risk"," assessment",","," and"," proactive"," measures",","," we"," can"," strive"," for"," a"," future"," with"," safer"," and"," more"," reliable"," self","-","driving"," car"," technology","."," ","\n\n","Would"," you"," like"," me"," to"," expand"," on"," any"," of"," the"," points"," or"," discuss"," other"," aspects"," of"," self","-","driving"," cars","?"],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"cohere","label":1}